Class RegNewAccountP2Controller

  • java.lang.Object
    • managment.RegNewAccountP2Controller

  • public class RegNewAccountP2Controller
extends java.lang.Object
    Class for the second part of user registration here the user entersr private account details or business account details, once user presses create the account is created data for account is taken from P1 Controller. user has an option between private account,business account or both.
